 agents. Having traveled all across the country and the world, she finds it easy to identify with people from all backgrounds. Terri&#8217;s clients consider her not only likable, but honest and trustworthy, and are eager to recommend her.<\/p><p style=\"text-align: start;\">Terri Michelle, REALTOR\u00ae<\/p><p style=\"text-align: start;\">Graduate, REALTOR\u00ae Institute (GRI) \u2022 Military Relocation Professional (MRP) \u2022 Pricing Strategy Advisor (PSA) \u2022 Real Estate Negotiation Expert (RENE) \u2022 Texas Affordable Housing Specialist-Divorce (RECS) \u2022 Accredited Buyer&#8217;s Representative (ABR\u00ae) \u2022 Seniors Real Estate Specialist\u00ae (SRES\u00ae) \u2022 Texas Residential Leasing Specialist (TRLS)\u00a0<\/p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><strong style=\"text-align: justify;\">Email:<\/strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> <span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"text-align: justify; color: #3366ff;\" href=\"mailto:TerriMichelleSunCity@gmail.com\">TerriMichelleSunCity@gmail.com<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f0e2410 elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"2f0e2410\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<style>\n.elementor-column.elementor-col-33 ul.elementor-icon-list-items {\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n}    \n<\/style>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Agents Terri Michelle Sales Associate Contact With a keen mind and a servant&#8217;s heart, Terri has dedicated her life and career as a REALTOR\u00ae\u00a0to serving her community. Her commitment to joyfully making a difference in the lives of others each day is reflected in both her professional and personal life. Terri has been inv